				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1580" class="elementor-element elementor-element-ac21a8d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="ac21a8d" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-c64ff4a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="c64ff4a" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>All chauffeurs undergo rigorous background checks, defensive driving certification, and non-disclosure training. They are professionals committed to absolute discretion and passenger privacy.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1581" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="2" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1581" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> How are chauffeurs monitored during a trip? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1581" class="elementor-element elementor-element-5c1beeb e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="5c1beeb" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-200526e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="200526e" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>Our 24/7 operations center monitors chauffeur performance through real-time data and GPS tracking.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1582" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="3" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1582" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Do chauffeurs assist with tasks beyond driving? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1582" class="elementor-element elementor-element-95133ce e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="95133ce" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ca913fe elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="ca913fe" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>Chauffeurs provide full-service luggage handling and door-to-door assistance for every passenger. They act as a mobile concierge, prepared to manage immediate logistics or itinerary adjustments as required.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1583" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="4" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1583" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Can the chauffeur assist with sensitive document handling? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1583" class="elementor-element elementor-element-747f2e7 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="747f2e7" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-40c411e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="40c411e" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>Chauffeurs are trained in strict non-disclosure protocols to ensure total privacy for all corporate discussions. They act as a discreet extension of your professional team throughout the duration of the journey.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1584" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="5" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1584" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Are chauffeurs trained in specific security or defensive driving? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1584" class="elementor-element elementor-element-0ed2f20 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="0ed2f20" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b854f55 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="b854f55" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>Our team completes specialized training in defensive driving techniques and emergency evasive maneuvers. This expertise ensures passenger safety remains uncompromised regardless of road or traffic conditions.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1585" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="6" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1585" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Can I request a female or a specific chauffeur? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1585" class="elementor-element elementor-element-22f5b7e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="22f5b7e" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-38ca51b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="38ca51b" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>We will certainly try to accommodate; however, this cannot be guaranteed and depends on availability.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				</div>
		</div><div id="jet-tabs-content-8083" class="jet-tabs__content " data-tab="3" role="tabpanel" aria-hidden="true" data-template-id="4414">		<div data-elementor-type="container" data-elementor-id="4414" class="elementor elementor-4414" data-elementor-post-type="elementor_library">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-da293d4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent" data-id="da293d4" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6739b67 elementor-widget elementor-widget-n-accordion" data-id="6739b67" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;default_state&quot;:&quot;all_collapsed&quot;,&quot;max_items_expended&quot;:&quot;one&quot;,&quot;n_accordion_animation_duration&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;ms&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:400,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]}}" data-widget_type="nested-accordion.default">
							<div class="e-n-accordion" aria-label="Accordion. Open links with Enter or Space, close with Escape, and navigate with Arrow Keys">
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1080" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="1" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1080" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> What areas do you service? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1080" class="elementor-element elementor-element-0c5aa2d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="0c5aa2d" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-153ddae elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="153ddae" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>Empire Limousine provides professional chauffeur services in over 600 cities worldwide, including all major global destinations and airports. Our network spans North America, Europe, the Middle East, Asia, and beyond—ensuring seamless transportation wherever your travels take you.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1081" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="2" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1081" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> How do I make a reservation? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1081" class="elementor-element elementor-element-fcbdd46 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="fcbdd46" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0509f14 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="0509f14" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>You can book directly through our <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://empirelimousines.com/online-reservation/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">booking page</a>,</span> by phone, or by contacting our reservations team.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1082" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="3" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1082" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> How far in advance should I book? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1082" class="elementor-element elementor-element-2175405 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="2175405" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5fa4dad elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="5fa4dad" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>We recommend booking as early as possible to ensure availability, especially during peak travel times.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1083" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="4" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1083" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Can I make last-minute reservations? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1083" class="elementor-element elementor-element-709a139 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="709a139" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-54ab67b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="54ab67b" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>Yes, we do accept last-minute bookings based on availability.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1084" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="5" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1084" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Can I schedule recurring transfers for executive commutes? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1084" class="elementor-element elementor-element-32b47b1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="32b47b1" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8fb78fa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="8fb78fa" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>Our system supports automated recurring reservations for consistent daily or weekly itineraries. You may modify or pause these schedules at any time via your dedicated account manager or our 24/7 concierge desk.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1085" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="6" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1085" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Do you provide transfers for private aviation and FBOs? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1085" class="elementor-element elementor-element-0347625 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="0347625" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6ec19fa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="6ec19fa" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>We coordinate directly with flight crews and FBO ground staff to facilitate tarmac-side or terminal-side pickups. Your chauffeur is positioned and ready the moment the aircraft door opens.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1086" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="7" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1086" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> What is the airport pickup procedure? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1086" class="elementor-element elementor-element-a4e5c7c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="a4e5c7c" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-912ac15 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="912ac15" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>Your chauffeur will meet you at the designated pickup location. Meet &amp; greet service is available upon request.</p><p>Complimentary wait time is included for airport pickups (typically 30–60 minutes, depending on airport type).</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1087" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="8" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1087" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> How do you track flights, and managed fluctuations? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1087" class="elementor-element elementor-element-794c505 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="794c505" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9986ec6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="9986ec6" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>We utilize real-time FAA flight tracking to adjust arrival times automatically for delays or early landings. Your chauffeur will be on-site and prepared the moment you deplane.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1088" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="9" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1088" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Will I receive a confirmation? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1088" class="elementor-element elementor-element-cd4985d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="cd4985d" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-214bf36 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="214bf36" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>Yes, once your reservation is confirmed, you will receive a confirmation email with all trip details.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-1089" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="10" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-1089" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Can I modify my reservation? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-1089" class="elementor-element elementor-element-9d3a925 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="9d3a925" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ba15768 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="ba15768" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p style="font-weight: 400;">Yes, modifications can be made prior to your scheduled pickup time, subject to availability.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-10810" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="11" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-10810" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> What is your cancellation policy? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-10810" class="elementor-element elementor-element-e45be26 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="e45be26" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e610247 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="e610247" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p style="font-weight: 400;">Cancellations must be made within the specified time frame to avoid charges. Policies may vary depending on vehicle type and service.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				</div>
		</div><div id="jet-tabs-content-8084" class="jet-tabs__content " data-tab="4" role="tabpanel" aria-hidden="true" data-template-id="4422">		<div data-elementor-type="container" data-elementor-id="4422" class="elementor elementor-4422" data-elementor-post-type="elementor_library">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-da293d4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent" data-id="da293d4" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e0bc33a elementor-widget elementor-widget-n-accordion" data-id="e0bc33a" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;default_state&quot;:&quot;all_collapsed&quot;,&quot;max_items_expended&quot;:&quot;one&quot;,&quot;n_accordion_animation_duration&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;ms&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:400,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]}}" data-widget_type="nested-accordion.default">
							<div class="e-n-accordion" aria-label="Accordion. Open links with Enter or Space, close with Escape, and navigate with Arrow Keys">
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-2350" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="1" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-2350" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> How quickly are trip receipts issued? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-2350" class="elementor-element elementor-element-0b3d87e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="0b3d87e" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-cb61593 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="cb61593" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p style="font-weight: 400;">Digital receipts are generated automatically and delivered to your designated email immediately upon trip completion. You may also access historical billing data through your secure corporate dashboard.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-2351" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="2" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-2351" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Do you provide consolidated billing for corporate accounts? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-2351" class="elementor-element elementor-element-e10f893 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="e10f893" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6ead599 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="6ead599" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p style="font-weight: 400;">Corporate partners receive monthly consolidated invoices tailored to internal accounting structures. Our portal allows for department-level tracking and seamless expense management.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-2352" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="3" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-2352" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> How does the charging work? Do you offer hourly "As-Directed" services? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-2352" class="elementor-element elementor-element-aad6628 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="aad6628" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-664b53b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="664b53b" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p style="font-weight: 400;">Our &#8220;As-Directed&#8221; service provides a dedicated chauffeur and late-model vehicle for any duration. This option allows for total itinerary flexibility and immediate adjustments as your schedule evolves.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-2353" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="4" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-2353" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> Are tolls and airport fees included in the initial quote? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-2353" class="elementor-element elementor-element-b8bde0d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="b8bde0d" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f09d240 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="f09d240" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p style="font-weight: 400;">All predictable expenses are integrated into our transparent pricing model prior to dispatch. This eliminates administrative surprises and ensures a seamless billing experience for your accounting department.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-2354" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="5" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-2354" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> How can I contact customer support? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-2354" class="elementor-element elementor-element-911a635 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="911a635" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e6e1de8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="e6e1de8" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p style="font-weight: 400;">You can reach our team via phone, email, or through our website contact form.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
						<details id="e-n-accordion-item-2355" class="e-n-accordion-item" >
				<summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="6" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-2355" >
					<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><div class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text"> What if I need assistance during my trip? </div></span>
							<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>
			<span class='e-opened' ><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-minus-icon lucide-minus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path></svg></span>
			<span class='e-closed'><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></span>
		</span>

						</summary>
				<div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-2355" class="elementor-element elementor-element-6d07825 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="6d07825" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-49f948a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="49f948a" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p style="font-weight: 400;">You can contact your chauffeur directly or reach our 24/7 support team for immediate assistance.</p>								</div>
				</div>
					</details>
					</div>
						</div>
				</div>
				</div>
		</div>			</div>
